'222\t' + _x("npc conversation", "The Monolith overlooks the Silver road that leads from Silver Cove to Free Haven.  It's been an object of fascination and occasional worship for ages.  A long time ago, some group of druids carved a home out of the giant rock, and it has been inhabited by various groups since then.  The druids who currently live there were experimenting with some kind of new magic, and I think something may have gone wrong.  They've been avoiding contact with the outside world for some time now, and refuse to allow visitors to enter the Monolith.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "The Monolith") + '\t\r\n'
