'422\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Although they were a heretical religion, their heart was in the right place.  The Church helped the poor, healed the sick, and comforted the distraught.  But they grew rich, powerful, and prideful, and pride indeed goeth before a fall.  When they attacked their rival, the Church of the Moon, they brought both their enemy and themselves down.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Church of the Sun") + '\r\n'
