'439\t' + _x("npc conversation", "When the storms hit in July, I was completely unprepared for the demand for winter clothes.  Now that I'm ready for the winter demand, it hasn't been all that cold.  I must have done something to anger the Heavens!") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Weather") + '\r\n'
