'554\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Diplomacy is the skill that makes people feel more favorable towards you.  If you must speak with someone who doesn't seem to like you, make sure that you use your most diplomatic person to do the talking.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Diplomacy") + '\r\n'
