'556\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I'm certain the devils destroyed the town of Sweet Water!  It was the most northwestern town in Enroth, and certainly one of the most beautiful.  Not many people made it out that way to visit, but now you don't hear anything about the place.  ") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Sweet Water") + '\r\n'
