'558\t' + _x("npc conversation", "The lords themselves are too busy to handle most affairs of state, so they have council members that attend the High Council in Free Haven for them.  Each lord has one council member, and these six people make most of the laws of the state, in the names of their respective lords.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Council Members") + '\r\n'
'559\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Plate armor is, of course, the strongest kind of armor available.  There is a legendary suit of armor called Zeus, and it can imbue its wearer with extraordinary strength, but it doesn’t do much for the personality.  ") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Magic Armor") + '\r\n'
