'561\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I know I charge a lot to travel with, but I'm worth it!  If you keep me around, I'll tell you words of wisdom you'll not soon hear from anyone else.  For instance, did you know that a fool and his money are soon parted?") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "A Fool's services") + '\r\n'
