'567\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Wise men are saying they think the Temple of Baa is behind all the disasters that have been happening recently.  I think they're probably right.  The temple offers free healing, but you should think twice before using it– people are suspicious of the temple, and you'll get a bad reputation for having anything to do with them.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Evil Temples") + '\r\n'
