'579\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I know it sounds bad, but the best job I ever had was Imperial Tax Collector for his Highness, Hareck IX.  We collected tax on a lot of ships, and good old Hareck always let us keep some of the booty– er, I mean proceeds.  <sighs> Yep.  Those were the days!") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Imperial Taxation") + '\r\n'
