'616\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Everyone has heard of Abdul's chain of discount stores.  Well, he also has an island resort where the old and tired can be rejuvenated for a hefty fee.  They say that Abdul himself lives on his resort Island and rarely visits the mainland.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Abdul's Discount Island Resort") + '\r\n'
'617\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Druidic orders flourish in the grasslands near Silver Cove.  These druids will often arrange stone circles to perform ceremonies or worship nature.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Druids ") + '\r\n'
'618\t' + _x("npc conversation", "The mountains that make up the gap that leads to Paradise Valley are called the Sentinels.  Folk tales suggest they protected the valley from evil; now they serve as a warning to anyone foolish enough to want to enter.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Sentinels ") + '\r\n'
'619\t' + _x("npc conversation", "There are many islands that can only be reached with a combination of boat travel and the Walk on Water spell.  Many of them are inhabited by the most horrible of monsters, but often the finest treasures can be found on them.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Islands") + '\r\n'
'620\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Travel by boat isn't instantaneous; it takes time.  Don't forget to factor in your travel times if you're running on a deadline.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Boat Travel") + '\r\n'
